description: This course is about modeling in blender ,if you are a beginner in blender and you want to learn modeling you should to watch this course.In this course you have learn how to model a tv.In this course materials are videos,all videos are under 20 minutes in 6 parts.Is simple to follow and understand.At the end of curse you have to now basics of modeling.You have to put idea in the work.This course is good because we demonstrate different technices in 3d modeling field.If you are completely beginner don't afraid to take this course because we teach you all simplest way to understand clearly and fast.
title: Quick Start to Modeling in Blender 3d - Volume 1
